Package org.openmuc.pcharge.data

Class ChargePortInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openmuc.pcharge.data.ChargePortInfo
  • public class ChargePortInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    A ChargePort represents a status reading of a charging station port. ChargePort is immutable. It contains a user, a timestamp, a status and additional information about the charging station port.
